{"tid":1214504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文有文鬥] 高官/建制/廢老 －如果凍結銀行戶口 (金融犯罪)","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:34:38.000Z","uid":71037,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab1b025fef28f74a779a7d719072f5ca9543966","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"新post 新台 － 朋友分享左好多有關銀行的冷知識，有關銀行Financial Crime Risk (金融犯罪合規) 既常識比我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>目的：</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 舉報可疑人士 － 例如某高官/建制/廢中/廢老 的可疑銀行戶口交易 &amp; 活動<br />\n2. 保護香港銀行業！不做洗黑錢逃犯天堂！ (估下全香港有幾多高官/建制/廢中/廢老有某香港銀行巨頭戶口呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 身體力行到銀行舉報可疑戶口，查都查死佢地</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 大目標：凍結可疑人士不論高官/建制/廢中/廢老 主要本地銀行戶口</span></span></strong> (建議大家去中環總行舉報！中環總行staff 出名質素高同專業，一定妥善處理舉報！)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>原理：</strong><br />\n1. 原來任何普通市民(你同我) 都有權向銀行舉報可疑銀行帳戶。<br />\n2. 某香港銀行巨頭集團致力保護香港銀行體系、免被利用作為 洗黑錢(Money Laundering) 或逃稅等金融犯罪平台。<br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">只要你有可疑人士既全名 + 身份證ID/Passport ID 或 account number</span>，而且有充分理據，你就有權向銀行職員舉報 － 要求佢必須要開file 調查。<br />\n2. 強調一定要開 &ldquo;SAR&rdquo; (Suspicious Account Report) 或 &ldquo;UAR&rdquo; (Unusual Account Report)。<br />\n3. 巨頭銀行出名嚴格查家宅，保證問你一輪再freeze 可疑account，以保護香港銀行免被奸人利用處理來歷不明既現金或資產。<br />\n<strong>4. 如果發現身邊有人疑似洗黑錢/逃稅/資金來歷不明 － <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家一齊去銀行分行向職員舉報！</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n朋友發夢見到如何搜查個人資料：<br />\n1. 土地查冊 (Land Search)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.iris.gov.hk/eservices/welcome.jsp?language=zh_TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.iris.gov.hk%2Feservices%2Fwelcome.jsp%3Flanguage%3Dzh_TW&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=7a11be9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.iris.gov.hk/eservices/welcome.jsp?language=zh_TW</a><br />\n2. 公司註冊處 (icris) - 可以查董事名單，順便舉報埋可疑公司戶口<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.icris.cr.gov.hk/csci/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icris.cr.gov.hk%2Fcsci%2F&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=db7b4e84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icris.cr.gov.hk/csci/</a><br />\n3. 查車牌 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130122/18142375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130122%2F18142375&d=lXSk0n6jiDV9AqJ6X6RhLt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=6554221d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130122%2F18142375&h=52aa2385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130122/18142375</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">何謂可疑人士呢?</span><br />\n1. 明明係維園呀伯，日日淨係鬧80後搞亂香港，但自己又無工返，<span style=\"color: red;\">無正職收入</span>，但戶口竟然有錢 － 請問資金來源何來？有無合理解釋d 存款點來? <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">資金來源是否黑錢？</span></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 50 幾歲貨車司機月入只有一萬幾，戶口竟然有幾百萬？唔通做好多秘撈收現金(e.g. 遊行) 再存入銀行？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有逃稅風險！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 頻繁現金交易 (有逃稅風險)<br />\n4. 戶口持有人無法說明資金來源<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家一齊去銀行舉報可疑人士，保護香港銀行業！不做洗黑錢逃犯天堂！</span></span>"},{"pid":"96b26e6f2a74c1efccfb63ae68edaca8a76a60fa","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"大家千萬不要做犯法野！<br />\n要做奉公守法好市民！"},{"pid":"32e3cf572e0ed4db9fc1b3380220c8d835cdb46b","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:37:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ed3a1796ca8e582042932475ecca6f54518c2b0","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"654c1ac7ee3d0ec630d7830667f9442c2d2b2c72","tid":1214504,"uid":3440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:39:14.000Z","msg":"呢鋪正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9e7a05dd975657b8bce6769e7652007c850531","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"齊舉報可疑人士"},{"pid":"192448e6b67604610a37a3e7846c6da04f44e77f","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91050bf9233604cd420c27675a213b221d949b15","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"幫手"},{"pid":"287759ab85bc30dc63a195b140ae6a5948f7b8c1","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"246e4f280f02491f40d59a45735e0d9c709e864b","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"931f61dde6e3e9aee1b3b898b7adf479cf95933e","tid":1214504,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"求實測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5017c6346dedbe6305e9e4a16b4444982d6f674","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"931f61dde6e3e9aee1b3b898b7adf479cf95933e","tid":1214504,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"求實測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"朋友實測過一次<br />\n有人秒撈做生意但要人入數自己既個人戶口<br />\n朋友親身到銀行分行舉報後，結果一個月後被人close account<br />\n果一個月期間完全用唔到"},{"pid":"1d7295ed14b180348fbb679fcc373da117b2261b","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:49:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d3c6b6f84b4385a9e019c109c1a86501994d7bc","tid":1214504,"uid":120484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef87ef39965dcc358a41af2c348b885582d6b4a9","tid":1214504,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}